span class='ls'>Verz. d. Oxf. H. 267,b,26</span>&nbsp;. <span class='ls' title='Verz. d. Oxf. H.'>286,a, No. 670</span>&nbsp;. <span class='sdata'>saṃdhyāṅgajapavidhi</span> 267,b,30. <span class='sdata'>˚mauna</span> 85,a,34. <span class='sdata'>˚niyama</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>BHĀG. P. 3,14,36</span>&nbsp;. Hier und da kann auch <span>Bed.</span> </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'> d〉 gemeint sein. </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— b〉 <i>Morgen</i>- oder <i>Abendgebet</i>: <span class='sdata'>pūrvāṃ</span> (<span class='sdata'>paścimāṃ</span>) <span class='sdata'>saṃdhyāṃ japan</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>M. 2,101. fg.</span>&nbsp; <span class='ls' title='M.'>4,93</span>&nbsp;. <span class='sdata'>ubhe saṃdhye japan</span> <span class='ls' title='M.'>2,222</span>&nbsp;. &nbsp;<span class='ls'>R. 1,25,20</span>&nbsp;. &nbsp;<span class='ls'>BRAHMA-P. in LA. (III) 54,7</span>&nbsp;. <span class='sdata'>˚prayoga</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Verz. d. Oxf. H. 93,a,4 v. u.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— c〉 <i>die Morgendämmerung</i> (<span>vgl.</span> <span class='sdata'>saṃdhyāṃśa</span>) <i>eines</i> <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Yuga</span> (<i>Weltperiode</i>) &nbsp;<span class='ls'>M. 1,69. fg.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>HARIV. 511. fgg.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>VP. 23</span>&nbsp;. &nbsp;<span class='ls'>BHĀG. P. 3,11,20</span>&nbsp;. <i>die Dämmerung am Anfange und am Ende eines</i> <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Yuga</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MED.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>HARIV. 11304</span>&nbsp;. <i>am Ende</i> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>BHĀG. P. 1,3,25</span>&nbsp;. </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— d〉 <i>die drei Gelenke des Tages: Morgen, Mittag und Abend</i>: <span class='sdata'>˚traya</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>VARĀH. BṚH. S. 34,8</span>&nbsp;. <i>die Genien dieser Zeitabschnitte</i> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>ĀŚV. GṚHY. PARIŚ. 1,2</span>&nbsp;. </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— e〉 <i>die Dämmerung</i> (<span>insbes.</span> <i>die Abenddämmerung</i>) personificirt als eine Manifestation <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Brahman</span>ʼs &nbsp;<span class='ls'>VP. 40</span>&nbsp;. &nbsp;<span class='ls'>BHĀG. P. 3,20,33. fgg.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>TROYER</span>&nbsp;_zu_&nbsp;<span class='ls'>RĀJA-TAR. 1,33</span>&nbsp;. als Geliebte der Sonne &nbsp;<span class='ls'>Spr. (II) 760</span>&nbsp;. <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Śiva</span>ʼs &nbsp;<span class='ls'>KATHĀS. 1,44</span>&nbsp;. &nbsp;<span class='ls'>RĀJA-TAR. 1,33</span>&nbsp;. <span class='ls' title='RĀJA-TAR.'>7,1</span>&nbsp;. als Gattin <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Kāla</span>ʼs &nbsp;<span class='ls'>VAIV. P.</span>&nbsp;_im_&nbsp;<span class='ls'>ŚKDR.</span>&nbsp; <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Pulastya</span>ʼs &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBH. 5,3970</span>&nbsp;. <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Pūṣan</span>ʼs [Page7-0647] &nbsp;<span class='ls'>R. 5,25,27</span>&nbsp;. als Schwieger <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Vidyutkeśa</span>ʼs <span class='ls' title='R.'>7,4,20. fg.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— f〉 <span>Bez.</span> <i>eines einjährigen Mädchens, das bei der</i> <span style='letter-spacing:2px;'>Durgā</span>- <i>Feier diese Göttin vertritt</i>, &nbsp;<span class='ls'>ANNADĀKALPA</span>&nbsp;_im_&nbsp;<span class='ls'>ŚKDR.</span>&nbsp; unter <span class='sdata'>kumārī</span>. </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— g〉 <span>N. pr.</span> eines Flusses &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MED.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>MBH. 2,375</span>&nbsp;. </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— h〉 <i>Grenze</i> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— i〉 = <span class='sdata'>saṃdhāna</span> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— k〉 <i>Versprechen, Gelöbniss</i> (fehlerhaft für <span class='sdata'>saṃdhā</span>) &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class='ls'>UJJVAL.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— l〉 = <span class='sdata'>cintā</span> (von <span class='hom' title='Homonym'>1.</span> <span class='sdata'>dhyā</span> mit <span class='sdata'>sam</span>) &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:2.0em;'>— m〉 <i>eine <span>best.</span> Blume</i> &nbsp;<span class='ls'>H. an.</span>&nbsp; </div><div style='padding-left:0.1em;'>— <span>Vgl.</span> <span class='sdata'>agrasaṃdhyā, upasaṃdhyam, trisaṃdhya, dīrgha˚, nīlasaṃdhyā, prāk˚</span> und <span class='sdata'>sāṃdhya</span>.</div>","evidence":{"band":4,"band_label":"attested -- look up","rank_all":35949,"count_all":2,"first_era":"Vedic","genre":null,"example":{"sa":"saṃdhye","ru":"сумерки","work":"manavadharmashastra","passage":"2.222","kind":"translation","source":"corpus_lexicon.jsonl (pwg_ru Phase 4, SanskritLexicography/RussianTranslation)"},"badges":[{"field":"band","value":4,"label":"attested -- look up","source":"kosha frequency layer, rank_all (DCS archive.sqlite M9 via VisualDCS)"},{"field":"count_all","value":2,"label":"2 attestations in DCS","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"first_era","value":"Vedic","label":"first attested: Vedic","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"genre","value":null,"label":"genre sketch not derivable from current DCS extraction (only a chronological period vector is stored, no per-genre breakdown)","source":"n/a -- gap documented, not fabricated (see app/evidence.py)"}]}}]}